            "subject": "Content Expiration Alert - December Batch",
            "body_plain": "Hi,\n\nThe following content assets are expiring soon and need your attention:\n\nPriority: Urgent (expires within 7 days)\n- Holiday Promo Banner - Expires: December 8, 2025\n\nPriority: Standard\n- Year-End Campaign Page - Expires: December 22, 2025\n- Winter Newsletter Template - Expires: December 28, 2025\n\nBatch: CXPA-226-Q4\n\nPlease review and take action on these items.",
